      "text": [
        " رَجُلٍ أَعْتَقَ بَعْضَ مَمْلُوكِهِ قَالَ \"هُوَ حُرٌّ كُلُّهُ لَيْسَ لِلَّهِ عَزَّ وَ جَلَّ شَرِيكٌ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3521 - It is narrated by Talhah bin Zayd, from Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) from his father, Imam Muhammad ibn Ali Al-Baqir (as), peace be upon him, regarding a man who freed part of his slave.\nImam (as) said: \"He is completely free; there is no partner with Allah (swt), the Almighty.\""
        ]
      }
